----------------------------------------------------------------
Comp Matrix parent . Find
----------------------------------------------------------------

	Element a        C1 WORD * a type
	Element b        C1 WORD * a type
	Element c        C1 WORD * a type
	Element pad      C1 WORD             * Padding
	Element search   C1 WORD             * Search for field

